{
  "stem": "945.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The rabbi [NON-ENGLISH], of course, left before the Soviet Union, before the Soviet Union took over.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was given information, which they told him to get out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he left, but [NON-ENGLISH] stayed on, carried on his duties.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he marched with his family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had a large family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And other prominent Jewish people marched with him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And everybody was walking towards the station.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Under the railroad tracks at the station, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] lot of cars, freight cars-- a cross between freight cars and cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't know at that time what they were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But there were cars, empty cars.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Lots of them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I don't know how many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Hundreds.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] the people of Vyshnivets [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Juden ?] started to assemble in great numbers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember that I wanted to go back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I wanted to see what Vyshnivets was like without [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] without its [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Juden. ?] And I was a young kid at that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I now know and understand what I felt, because it was a ghost town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They tore the Jewish heart out of it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Anyway, I returned to the station, and joined my family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And they told us to get into the cars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Crowded us into the cars.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I don't remember how many-- 40-50 in a car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "With our [NON-ENGLISH], our belongings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Belongings.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We sat on the belongings; we were almost up to the top.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was a little window for air.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so they packed us all off, and the train started.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The train started.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
